\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{k=0}^{n}z^{k}b_{k}$
\end_inset 

 of equation 
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq: geo series}

\end_inset 

.
\layout Standard

Note that the above is a proof of a series acceleration method for a more-or-les
