Winding in the opposite direction, one has 
\begin_inset Formula \[
g_{1}^{-1}\cdot\mbox{Li}_{s}\left(z\right)=\mbox{Li}_{s}\left(z\right)-\Delta_{-1}\]

\end_inset 

