 not on the critical strip.
\layout Standard

As 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset 

 increases, the remaining zeroes circle around in a widening spiral: thus,
 the zero at the far left of the image is not near 
\begin_inset Formula $z=-1$
\end_inset 

